\c 4
\s Uchenjeri hunopa imwe mibairo
\p
\v 1 Inzwai, vana, murairo wababa; uye muchenjerere kuti muzive kunzwisisa.
\v 2 Nokuti ndinokupai dzidziso yakanaka; regai kusiya murairo wangu.
\v 3 Nokuti ndaiva ndiri mwanakomana kuna baba vangu, ndakapfava, ndiri ndoga pamberi pamai vangu.
\v 4 Zvino vakandirairidza ndokuti kwandiri: Moyo wako ngaubatisise mashoko angu; chengeta mirairo yangu ugorarama.
\v 5 Wana uchenjeri, wana kunzwisisa; usakanganwa uye usatendeuka kubva pamashoko emuromo wangu.
\v 6 Usahusiya, uye huchakuchengetedza; uhude, zvino huchakurinda.
\v 7 Chekutanga uchenjeri; wana uchenjeri, uye nezvawawana zvose wana kunzwisisa.
\v 8 Uhukudze, zvino huchakukwiridzira; huchakuvigira rukudzo kana uchihumbundikira.
\v 9 Huchapa musoro wako chishongo chenyasha, huchakuvigira korona inobwinya.
\v 10 Inzwa, mwanakomana wangu, uye gamuchira mashoko angu; zvino makore eupenyu hwako achava mazhinji.
\v 11 Ndakakudzidzisa panzira yeuchenjeri; ndakakufambisa pamakwara ekururama.
\v 12 Kana uchifamba nhanho yako haingambandidzirwi; uye kana uchimhanya haungagumburwi.
\v 13 Batirira pakurairwa; usaregedza; ukuchengete, nokuti ndiko upenyu hwako.
\p
\v 14 Usapinda pagwara revakaipa, uye usafara munzira yevakaipa.
\v 15 Uinzvenge, usapfuura nemairi; tsauka pairi ugopfuura.
\v 16 Nokuti havarari kana vasina kuita chakaipa; uye hope dzavo dzinobviswa kana vasina kugumbura \add munhu\add*.
\v 17 Nokuti vanodya zvekudya zvezvakaipa, nekunwa waini yezvechisimba.
\v 18 Asi gwara revakarurama rakaita sechiedza chinopenya, chinofamba chichipenya kusvika pamasikati makuru.
\v 19 Nzira yevakaipa yakaita serima; havazivi kuti vachagumburwa nei.
\p
\v 20 Mwanakomana wangu, teerera mashoko angu; uise nzeve yako pakutaura kwangu.
\v 21 Ngazvirege kupukunyuka kubva pameso ako; uzvichengete mukati memoyo wako.
\v 22 Nokuti ndihwo upenyu kune vanoawana, neutano kumuviri wavo wose.
\p
\v 23 Chengeta moyo wako kupfuura zvose zvinochengetedzwa; nokuti mauri munobva kubuda kukuru kweupenyu.
\v 24 Bvisa kwauri kutsauka kwemuromo; uye kukombama kwemiromo isa kure newe.
\v 25 Meso ako ngaatarise mberi; nemafunhiro emeso ako arurame pamberi pako.
\v 26 Gadzira gwara rerutsoka rwako; uye nzira dzako dzose dzisimbe.
\v 27 Usarerekera kurudyi kana kuruboshwe; dzora rutsoka rwako pane zvakaipa.
